  "plot_summary": "While not technically an announcement, when it was pointed out by several readers who detected Steve Ditko's hand in an early issue of the <i>Hulk</i>, the editors admitted that Steve had helped ink that issue and stated in the letters page of [LINK:1962:HULK_5_hulk1|HULK #5], saying:\n\n<i>To save any future confusion, you have probably noticed that we are starting to name the writer, the artist, and inker (when there IS a separate inker) to all our feature strips from now on.&nbsp; Hope you fans like the idea.</i>",
